Package xbrlcore.linkbase

Class Summary
CalculationLinkbase This class represents the calculation linkbase of a DTS.
DefinitionLinkbase This class represents the definition linkbase of a DTS.
LabelLinkbase This class represents a label linkbase of a DTS.
Linkbase This class is a superclass for all classes implementing linkbases.
PresentationLinkbase This class represents a presentation linkbase of a DTS.
PresentationLinkbaseElement For each Concept in a taxonomy which appears in the presentation linkbase, there is one corresponding PresentationLinkbaseElement.
